section.section:
The public notice required by this subsection shall:
Be given at least once;
Appear at least 1 week, but not more than 30 days, before the final date for submitting bids;
If the contract pertains to bridge or road work, set forth the place where the bridge or road is to be constructed or repaired;
Set forth a description of the goods or services being bid on;
Provide notice that sealed proposals for the goods or services will be received until a day named in the advertisement; and
Provide notice of the date for the opening of the bids.
